      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUNDY ALL GO (2) had been racing well with a Restricted WIN win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Will find this more suitable and can atone. SPEEDOMETER (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 20.00 beating JADE CLOVER. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Has definite claims. GIVERNY (3) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (20.21) at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Has ability and can measure up. EXTRA VOLTAGE (6) won last start in very good time. Hard to beat again.",
